{"tid":1913084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天津武清區發生軍機墜毀事件","createTime":"2020-03-06T13:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T13:55:59.000Z","uid":167313,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd60f09710e612fe281e680ff1c2aa0446f9775","tid":1913084,"uid":167313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:50:11.000Z","msg":"網絡熱傳的一個視頻顯示，天津武清區3月5日發生軍機墜毀事件，現場火光熊熊，濃密的黑煙直衝天空，並持續傳出疑似爆炸聲。當前正是大陸局勢的敏感時刻，事發在北京周邊，引發網民聯想和熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n視頻裡，一名市民說，剛才人們都看見了，飛機掉下來了。飛行員跳傘。<br />\n<br />\n現場有不少市民圍觀。事件發生後不久，多輛警車及消防車抵達現場，同時現場不斷傳出疑似爆炸聲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一位市民說，飛機掉下來（爆）炸了！<br />\n<br />\n此消息迅速傳開，推特上不斷有網民轉發視頻並發表評論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VqE0nqC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVqE0nqC.png&h=9fc6344b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TRU0nqD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTRU0nqD.png&h=76c13338&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vuUC85D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvuUC85D.png&h=c4725216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/pk166\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fpk166&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=dc258c79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/pk166</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/yqtj3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fyqtj3&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=2e871ada\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/yqtj3</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/bfora\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fbfora&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=70ff73dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/bfora</a>"},{"pid":"cee9eacafaa8a57cdc75f7b972f1ff5a7f056842","tid":1913084,"uid":309935,"like":0,"dislike"